        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Expediting Federal Broadband Deployment Reviews Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the National Telecommunications and Information Administration to establish an interagency strike force to increase specified agencies' prioritization of reviews for communications use authorizations on federal property. A <i>communications use authorization</i> is an easement, right-of-way, lease, license, or other authorization to locate or modify a communications facility on certain public land.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
